  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>We're proud to say that the Chalet Hotel Breithorn is one of our properties run by our sister company Ski Total. Offering an authentic chalet experience with greater choice and quality in <a data-udi="umb://document/090d2ea7dadc4d03ba25ba2f7aaac686" href="/{localLink:umb://document/090d2ea7dadc4d03ba25ba2f7aaac686}" title="Champoluc">Champoluc</a>.</strong></p>
<p><span>The property is a lovely, traditional hotel which has been beautifully restored and modernised whilst respecting all its traditional Alpine features and character.</span></p>
<p><span>There is a spacious lounge with a small bar and reception area with an open flame fire, beautiful carved vaulted wooden ceilings and comfortable furniture on which to relax.</span></p>
<p><span>Off the lounge is a small library with a selection of books, perfect as a quiet place to read. There is also a sun terrace, on which you can enjoy some late afternoon sun and an après ski drink at the end of the day.</span></p>
<p><span>The restaurant is on the lower ground floor and is spacious and tastefully decorated, in accordance with the rest of the property. </span></p>
<p><span>The Chalet Hotel also has a Wellness Centre with sauna, steam room, whirlpool and massage showers which is a perfect retreat for skiers at the end of the day (Must be aged 16+ years). </span></p>]]></description>
